name: Precious Metal
description:
The 5th work in the 'Trophies' series, 'Precious Metal' reimagines a ceremonial monstrance as an artisanal tribute to the glories of heavy metal. 

A digital version of an original oil painting on wood. JPEG 2558 x 1567 px @ 300 dpi.

'Instruments to sight the stars, possibly I've seen too much'
